        "heading": "Attack Vector 2: Governance Whale Dominance",
        "content": "**The problem:*\n**Defense options:*Require 10% quorum AND 2/3 supermajority. Makes it harder to pass malicious proposals even with large holder.\n\n**Option B: Governance Mining (Retroactive Voting Power)*\n**Option C: Anti-Whale Measures (Radical Democracy)*\n**Option D: Guardian Veto (Centralized Backstop)*\n---"
