        "answer": "Yes — this is one of the most impactful applications. Most temp workers wait 1-2 weeks for payment after working because: client pays staffing agency on net-14 or net-30 terms, then agency processes payroll. With escrow-funded contracts, client pre-funds the assignment, and workers receive payment the same day timesheets are approved, regardless of the agency's bank processing cycle."
