        "question": "What is the minimum viable tokenization platform?",
        "answer": "Minimum: one security token contract (transfer restrictions, whitelist), one KYC integration (Parallel Markets or VerifyInvestor), one distribution function, investor dashboard showing balance and distribution history. Cost: $80,000–$120,000. Full platform with secondary market: $185,000–$375,000."
