        "heading": "H1: GameFi Esports Infrastructure — Trustless Prize Pools, Ranking Systems, and Tournament Brackets",
        "content": "**H2: Blockchain enables trustless esports: prize pools held in smart contracts, verifiable rankings, and automatic payouts. Here is the complete infrastructure architecture.*"
