        "heading": "Revenue Model 4: Protocol-Owned Liquidity (POL)",
        "content": "Rather than renting liquidity (paying emissions to LPs who may exit), the protocol permanently acquires LP positions using treasury funds.\n\n**OlympusDAO mechanism (2021–2022):*\n**What POL solves:*\n**What POL does not solve:*\n---"
