        "heading": "H1: GameFi Smart Contract Suite — Complete Implementation of Token, NFT, Staking, and Tournament",
        "content": "**H2: A complete GameFi system requires four contract categories: governance token, utility token, NFT items, and game mechanics (staking, tournament, crafting). Here is the full architecture and how the contracts interact.*"
