        "heading": "Mitigation Strategies",
        "content": "**1. Stablecoin pairs (no IL):*\n**2. Concentrated liquidity ranges:*\n**3. Correlated asset pairs:*\n**4. Single-asset yield (avoid IL entirely):*\n---"
