        "heading": "H1: Flash Loan Attack Simulation — Testing Every DeFi Protocol Function for Flash Loan Exploitability",
        "content": "**H2: Before your auditor does, simulate flash loan attacks against every public function in your protocol. Here is the framework we use for all DeFi protocol security reviews.*"
