        "content": "### H1: Web3 Development Company — Decentralized Applications Built for Business, Not Demos\n\n**H2: We have been building on the decentralized web since 2014 — before it was called Web3. 1,000+ blockchain projects delivered. We build dApps, Web3 platforms, and DAO infrastructure that generates revenue, retains users, and operates at scale.*\n**Trust indicators:*\n**[BUTTON — PRIMARY] Book a Free Strategy Call →*\n**[BUTTON] Download Web3 Capability Deck →*",
